{"tid":827632,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【山竹過後】地下車場積水汽車泊路邊　廣州交警颱風翌晨即抄牌捱轟　","createTime":"2018-09-19T05:23:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T06:50:02.000Z","uid":153228,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3affafdb70adf08189658e10d8b17d7836ec03c0","tid":827632,"uid":153228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:23:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00004/1537230427104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00004%2F1537230427104&d=5RgmMYkHYhMYhPq%2FaWXbszOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=7b708dc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180918%2Fs00004%2F1537230427104&h=84a2bfc5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180918/s00004/1537230427104</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180918/s00004/24b0e87ae6c603a00332857235c3e8cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180918%2Fs00004%2F24b0e87ae6c603a00332857235c3e8cf.jpg&h=de7c267c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強颱風「山竹」周日（18日）橫掃華南沿岸，多個城市滿目瘡痍，交通大受影響。然而有廣州網民昨晨（17日）發現「山竹」威脅剛剛遠去不久，便有交通警於海珠區拍攝路邊臨時停泊車輛，似是抄牌，惹起熱議。<br />\n<br />\n這名網民表示，過去颱風吹襲時，他們所住小區的地下停車場經常積水，故管理公司這次預先提醒車主，將車輛駛往路面臨時停放。然而昨日清晨8時半左右，「山竹」剛剛遠去，颱風預警信號仍未完全除下時，便有交通警在路邊抄牌。<br />\n<br />\n他透露曾向這名交警多次協商，但對方卻不為所動，他質疑在此特殊情況下，短暫佔用路面資源是否完全不可取。<br />\n<br />\n片段流傳後惹來輿論熱議，廣州市公安交警部門其後發聲明，認為地下停車場有安全隱患，故考慮實際情況後，決定對這名交警收集到的違泊紀錄不予審核通過，並向車主致歉。同時，其他因惡劣天氣緊急避險或無法判斷交通信號指示等，而被監控設備收集到的違法紀錄，當局亦承諾不予審核通過。<br />\n<br />\n（澎湃新聞）"},{"pid":"50b622b1fcf7001b0484e3840bf9a53aa3088ff7","tid":827632,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T05:37:43.000Z","msg":"香港警察都捉人亂過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6854118da553b18cc54c224f5fd66827f22033aa","tid":827632,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"呢個仆街心諗今鋪FATFAT啦，抄咁多牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好明顯要追數"},{"pid":"746c7cd013d62c013423883a42c95e0905267878","tid":827632,"uid":37069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:24:47.000Z","msg":"周日（18日）"},{"pid":"2f7a9ac6fcc9ae99a27186fbfd163c33f158706d","tid":827632,"uid":28743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"部車無積到水 黨已經幫你省左一筆<br />\n炒你個牌拎返少少錢係度嘈嘈嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再嘈捉你打把屌你老母"},{"pid":"8ccdc2085e7e2b212839c68e62149af4ff5afcf9","tid":827632,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:35:07.000Z","msg":"等錢洗嘛"},{"pid":"99bf9d28f9adc0d7cf92036c0296a50bdb508867","tid":827632,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746f91beeb1b2b76e534f1b3aebcece470b51a83","tid":827632,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"唔怕比車主打  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}